      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presented here is a truly exceptional example of a vehicle that has been maintained to the highest possible standard. This car looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no swirls, chips, or door dings to be found. Every body panel is original and perfectly aligned. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of cleanliness; the premium leather seats remain supple with no bolster wear, and the interior still carries that fresh, new-car scent. It has been a strictly smoke-free and pet-free environment. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a full binder of service records, documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. The engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts with seamless precision, and the tires are near-new with deep tread remaining. This is a turn-key, collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who refuses to settle for anything less than perfection. Garage-kept and sparingly driven in fair weather only.",
      "price": 46500.0,
